Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I wonder what this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this is a tooth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:40.22,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}I walk ten thousand miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:43.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}Ten thousand miles to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:50.09,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}And every gasp of breath I grabbed at just to find you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:55.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}And every single step of the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:58.28,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\alpha&HFF&}And every single step of the way, {\r\blur1.5}I pay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:05.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}Every single night and day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:10.21,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}I searched for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:14.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}Through sandstorms and hazy dawns,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1.5}I reached...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:21.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\alpha&HFF&}I reached... {\r\blur1.5}for you
