Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh seedling that sprouts from \Nour ancestor's flesh and blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,938)\i1}Grow green, green leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bear heavy, heavy seed.
